data.description:
This renovated Hilton Head Plantation home, with an $85k remodel, sits at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac on a spacious double lot (.8 ac). Updates include new plumbing, bathrooms, kitchen appliances, water heater, AC unit, and more. 

The expansive open floor plan flows nicely while connecting 3 bedrooms, a dining room, eat-in kitchen, den/office, laundry room, 2 baths, and a screened lanai. Features include a wood-burning fireplace and gas range. Enjoy outdoor space with privacy and golf/lagoon views, along with easy access to the community bike/walking path. Don't let this value-packed opportunity slip away…you’ll regret it later!
